_sText:
de_extraction is a port with remake of the cs_extraction map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

First Place Winner

of the 2020 Source Engine Discord Wingman Contest[www.sediscord.com].

ORIGINAL DESCRIPTION

Get to the choppa!

A man is being held hostage at his mansion on the Swedish skerries.

Secure him and take him to one of the TWO rescue zones to summon a helicopter.

Keep the landing area clear until the helicopter arrives and take out the hostage!

Designed for the follower, but can also be played 5v5.

- Now this map bomb defuse.
